**Summary**

- `my-claw/tools/senseweave/sampler_buffers.py`: added `capacity` (default 64) and an `OrderedDict[int, BufferRecord]` LRU index. `on_sampler_load` now evicts the LRU record (calling `/b_free` and clearing its `buffer_id`) when the live set is at capacity, then inserts the new record as MRU. `on_sampler_free` removes the record from the index. New `touch(record)` promotes a record to MRU on access; no-op when the record isn't tracked.
